        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 21 at 5:08PM EDT by NWS Buffalo NY</headline>
        <description>At 500 PM EDT, a line of strong thunderstorms was reported over
North Tonawanda and Clarence, moving northeast at 50 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 40 mph.

SOURCE...Radar.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects. Minor damage to outdoor objects is
possible.
</description>
